(49, '発音について(段)', '<p style=\"cursor: text; margin-top: 14px; margin-bottom: 14px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: rgb(66, 66, 66); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space: pre-wrap;\">前回の記事の結論は以下のとおりである。</p><p style=\"cursor: text; margin-top: 14px; margin-bottom: 14px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: rgb(66, 66, 66); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><br></p><p style=\"cursor: text; margin-top: 14px; margin-bottom: 14px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: rgb(66, 66, 66); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space: pre-wrap;\">各段の本能的な役割をまとめると、</p><p style=\"cursor: text; margin-top: 14px; margin-bottom: 14px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: rgb(66, 66, 66); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space: pre-wrap;\">「あ」中〜高／長 (高音は任せろ！)</p><p style=\"cursor: text; margin-top: 14px; margin-bottom: 14px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: rgb(66, 66, 66); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space: pre-wrap;\">「い」中／短 (細かい音符に雑に使える)</p><p style=\"cursor: text; margin-top: 14px; margin-bottom: 14px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: rgb(66, 66, 66); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space: pre-wrap;\">「う」低／長 (低音は任せろ！)</p><p style=\"cursor: text; margin-top: 14px; margin-bottom: 14px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: rgb(66, 66, 66); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space: pre-wrap;\">「え」やや低〜高／すべて (優等生)</p><p style=\"cursor: text; margin-top: 14px; margin-bottom: 14px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: rgb(66, 66, 66); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space: pre-wrap;\">「お」低〜中／すべて (低音が得意)</p><p style=\"cursor: text; margin-top: 14px; margin-bottom: 14px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: rgb(66, 66, 66); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space: pre-wrap;\">「ん」－／短 (溜めになって弾みがつく)</p><p style=\"cursor: text; margin-top: 14px; margin-bottom: 14px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: rgb(66, 66, 66); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><br></p><p style=\"cursor: text; margin-top: 14px; margin-bottom: 14px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: rgb(66, 66, 66); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space: pre-wrap;\">親しみ易く歌い易いVocalメロディーを作るには、この役割に従って歌詞を書けばいいわけだが、それだけではダメだということも、前回言及した。</p><p style=\"cursor: text; margin-top: 14px; margin-bottom: 14px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: rgb(66, 66, 66); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space: pre-wrap;\">本記事ではそれを具体的に考えていく。</p><p style=\"cursor: text; margin-top: 14px; margin-bottom: 14px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: rgb(66, 66, 66); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><br></p><p style=\"cursor: text; margin-top: 14px; margin-bottom: 14px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: rgb(66, 66, 66); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space: pre-wrap;\">たどり着いた結論を述べる。</p><p style=\"cursor: text; margin-top: 14px; margin-bottom: 14px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: rgb(66, 66, 66); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space: pre-wrap;\">歌詞の発音が本能的な役割に従わないとき、その歌はナルシスティックな、自己陶酔的な、キザな雰囲気を醸し出すと感じられる。</p><p style=\"cursor: text; margin-top: 14px; margin-bottom: 14px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: rgb(66, 66, 66); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><br></p><p style=\"cursor: text; margin-top: 14px; margin-bottom: 14px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: rgb(66, 66, 66); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space: pre-wrap;\">特筆すべきは</p><p style=\"cursor: text; margin-top: 14px; margin-bottom: 14px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: rgb(66, 66, 66); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space: pre-wrap;\">①低音の「あ」段、②低音あるいは高音の「い」段、③高音の「う」段、④長音の「ん」</p><p style=\"cursor: text; margin-top: 14px; margin-bottom: 14px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: rgb(66, 66, 66); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space: pre-wrap;\">だと思う。</p><p style=\"cursor: text; margin-top: 14px; margin-bottom: 14px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: rgb(66, 66, 66); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space: pre-wrap;\">モーニング娘。のI WISHのAメロは</p><p style=\"cursor: text; margin-top: 14px; margin-bottom: 14px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: rgb(66, 66, 66); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space: pre-wrap;\">「ひ(※②)とりぼっちですこし　たいくつ(※③)なよる　わたしだけがさびしいの　Ah(※①)　Uh～(※④)」となっている。</p><p style=\"cursor: text; margin-top: 14px; margin-bottom: 14px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: rgb(66, 66, 66); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space: pre-wrap;\">このAメロは自分の心の中を見つめるような自己陶酔的な美しさを感じる。発音に着目しても、このように、ナルシスティックな発音の使われ方が散見される。</p><p style=\"cursor: text; margin-top: 14px; margin-bottom: 14px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: rgb(66, 66, 66); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space: pre-wrap;\">　特に「く→つ」のように母音保続しながらストレスの大きい状態へと遷移すると、非常にエモーショナルだ。</p><p style=\"cursor: text; margin-top: 14px; margin-bottom: 14px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: rgb(66, 66, 66); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><img src=\"data:image/jpeg;base64,\" style=\"width: 700px;\" data-filename=\"RS=^ADB3LZ_k.jpg\"><br></p><p style=\"cursor: text; margin-top: 14px; margin-bottom: 14px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: rgb(66, 66, 66); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space: pre-wrap;\">PENICILLINのロマンスのサビは</p><p style=\"cursor: text; margin-top: 14px; margin-bottom: 14px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: rgb(66, 66, 66); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space: pre-wrap;\">「あいに(※②)きづいてください(※②)　ぼくが(※①)だきしめてあげる(※③)」</p><p style=\"cursor: text; margin-top: 14px; margin-bottom: 14px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: rgb(66, 66, 66); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space: pre-wrap;\">これは曲調と相まって、言わずもがな、非常にナルシスティックだ。</p><p style=\"cursor: text; margin-top: 14px; margin-bottom: 14px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: rgb(66, 66, 66); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><br></p><p style=\"cursor: text; margin-top: 14px; margin-bottom: 14px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: rgb(66, 66, 66); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space: pre-wrap;\">まとめると、発音には親しみ易く開放的な「本能的用法」とナルシスティックな「自己陶酔的用法」があ</p><p style=\"cursor: text; margin-top: 14px; margin-bottom: 14px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: rgb(66, 66, 66); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space: pre-wrap;\">るということになる。</p><p style=\"cursor: text; margin-top: 14px; margin-bottom: 14px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: rgb(66, 66, 66); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space: pre-wrap;\">平歌で後者をよく用い、サビでは前者</p><p style=\"cursor: text; margin-top: 14px; margin-bottom: 14px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: rgb(66, 66, 66); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space: pre-wrap;\">サビの1回し目で後者をよく用い、2回し目で前者</p><p style=\"cursor: text; margin-top: 14px; margin-bottom: 14px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: rgb(66, 66, 66); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space: pre-wrap;\">などの構成の技巧がよく見受けられる。</p>', '2022-09-26 06:29:58', '2022-09-26 06:29:58', 3);
